 additional freight explains the PnL improvement. The additional call to Veracruz obviously increased the port costs and bunker cost but, however these costs are covered in additional freight. All in all a fairly smooth voyage and interesting introduction to clean ops!"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-26T15:02:02.3","modifiedByFull":"Mohlin, Max","remark":"demurrage updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-13T19:38:55.75","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended stay at Veracruz"},{"modifiedDate":"2023-09-11T14:12:50.517","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional port added ECMX."}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}